About this thing:
=================

This stores a really simple template, that is sort of
based on the article from TeXLive. I also made a couple
of functions for typing differential equations and
checklists.

|   Tree of useful things:
|
|       |----- ..
|       |----- .
|       |----- diffeq.typ
|       |----- tasks.typ
|       |----- template.typ
|
